# Public Documentation (Visible on GitHub)
# ============================================
# Keep these files:
# - README.md (main project documentation)
# - CHANGELOG.md (version history)
# - RELEASE_*.md (release notes)
# - docs/README.md (documentation index)
# - docs/PUBLICATION_MATRIX.md (public/private documentation rules)
# - docs/SECURITY.md (responsible disclosure, no vulnerability details)
